<codeline><highlight class="normal">[example_apple_opengl2/](https://github.com/ocornut/imgui/blob/master/examples/example_apple_opengl2/)<sp/>&lt;BR&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">OSX<sp/>+<sp/>OpenGL2<sp/>example.<sp/>&lt;BR&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">=<sp/>main.mm<sp/>+<sp/>imgui_impl_osx.mm<sp/>+<sp/>imgui_impl_opengl2.cpp<sp/>&lt;BR&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">(NB:<sp/>imgui_impl_osx.mm<sp/>is<sp/>currently<sp/>not<sp/>as<sp/>feature<sp/>complete<sp/>as<sp/>other<sp/>platforms<sp/>backends.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/>You<sp/>may<sp/>prefer<sp/>to<sp/>use<sp/>the<sp/>GLFW<sp/>Or<sp/>SDL<sp/>backends,<sp/>which<sp/>will<sp/>also<sp/>support<sp/>Windows<sp/>and<sp/>Linux.)</highlight></codeline>
