<codeline><highlight class="normal">Note<sp/>that<sp/>other<sp/>examples<sp/>based<sp/>on<sp/>SDL<sp/>or<sp/>GLFW<sp/>+<sp/>OpenGL<sp/>could<sp/>easily<sp/>be<sp/>modified<sp/>to<sp/>work<sp/>with<sp/>Emscripten.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">We<sp/>provide<sp/>this<sp/>to<sp/>make<sp/>the<sp/>Emscripten<sp/>differences<sp/>obvious,<sp/>and<sp/>have<sp/>them<sp/>not<sp/>pollute<sp/>all<sp/>other<sp/>examples.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
