<codeline><highlight class="normal">This<sp/>uses<sp/>more<sp/>modern<sp/>OpenGL<sp/>calls<sp/>and<sp/>custom<sp/>shaders.<sp/>&lt;BR&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">This<sp/>may<sp/>actually<sp/>also<sp/>work<sp/>with<sp/>OpenGL<sp/>2.x<sp/>contexts!<sp/>&lt;BR&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Prefer<sp/>using<sp/>that<sp/>if<sp/>you<sp/>are<sp/>using<sp/>modern<sp/>OpenGL<sp/>in<sp/>your<sp/>application<sp/>(anything<sp/>with<sp/>shaders).</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
