<codeline><highlight class="normal">This<sp/>is<sp/>quite<sp/>long<sp/>and<sp/>tedious,<sp/>because:<sp/>Vulkan.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">For<sp/>this<sp/>example,<sp/>the<sp/>main.cpp<sp/>file<sp/>exceptionally<sp/>use<sp/>helpers<sp/>function<sp/>from<sp/>imgui_impl_vulkan.h/cpp.</highlight></codeline>
