<codeline><highlight class="normal">GLUT<sp/>(e.g.,<sp/>FreeGLUT<sp/>on<sp/>Linux/Windows,<sp/>GLUT<sp/>framework<sp/>on<sp/>OSX)<sp/>+<sp/>OpenGL2<sp/>example.<sp/>&lt;BR&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">=<sp/>main.cpp<sp/>+<sp/>imgui_impl_glut.cpp<sp/>+<sp/>imgui_impl_opengl2.cpp<sp/>&lt;BR&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Note<sp/>that<sp/>GLUT/FreeGLUT<sp/>is<sp/>largely<sp/>obsolete<sp/>software,<sp/>prefer<sp/>using<sp/>GLFW<sp/>or<sp/>SDL.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
