<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">However,<sp/>consider<sp/>that<sp/>OS<sp/>mouse<sp/>cursors<sp/>are<sp/>typically<sp/>drawn<sp/>through<sp/>a<sp/>very<sp/>specific<sp/>hardware<sp/>accelerated</highlight></codeline>
