<codeline><highlight class="normal">but<sp/>not<sp/>limited<sp/>to<sp/>Dear<sp/>ImGui<sp/>windows).<sp/>Because<sp/>UI<sp/>rendering<sp/>and<sp/>interaction<sp/>happens<sp/>on<sp/>the<sp/>same<sp/>plane</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">as<sp/>the<sp/>mouse,<sp/>that<sp/>disconnect<sp/>may<sp/>be<sp/>jarring<sp/>to<sp/>particularly<sp/>sensitive<sp/>users.</highlight></codeline>
